This provided visibility into an understanding of each other's workflows and unique challenges.

86
00:05:07,498 --> 00:05:13,841
So an artist gets to know what a designer's workflow is, and it develops trust, empathy,

87
00:05:14,481 --> 00:05:15,701
and they share common goals.

88
00:05:16,181 --> 00:05:21,083
So cross-discipline teamwork is where the real magic happens for creative teams, in

89
00:05:21,103 --> 00:05:21,863
my experience.

