00:12:32,324 --> 00:12:37,585
The teams were like fleets of sailboats, an armada, all heading to the same point.

216
00:12:38,825 --> 00:12:40,766
We just needed to coordinate them.

217
00:12:41,606 --> 00:12:48,987
