00:16:19,411 --> 00:16:21,872
You've got this ritual cadence.

267
00:16:23,732 --> 00:16:26,233
So I'm familiar with those, the Agile Scrum rituals,

268
00:16:26,293 --> 00:16:28,074
but those were actually to help teams

269
00:16:28,394 --> 00:16:30,095
stay aligned within themselves.

270
00:16:30,115 --> 00:16:33,116
You know, was there a ritual that could help

