00:24:46,195 --> 00:24:48,436
All of the content teams working on Destiny 2,

402
00:24:49,316 --> 00:24:52,897
300 people in the same location for a full day of planning,

403
00:24:53,458 --> 00:24:56,139
and face-to-face cross-team discussion, and agreement,

404
00:24:56,619 --> 00:24:57,259
and commitment.

