00:53:13,932 --> 00:53:15,113
Fucking awesome!

870
00:53:18,536 --> 00:53:20,297
Key takeaways I want to leave you with.

871
00:53:22,479 --> 00:53:26,762
The first one is as your game grows in size and complexity,

872
00:53:27,362 --> 00:53:31,145
the benefits of well-designed, well-executed sync rituals are huge.

873
00:53:32,706 --> 00:53:36,669
So whatever your size and complexity, whatever that growth is,

874
00:53:37,209 --> 00:53:39,992
whether it's from 5 people to 10 people, or 10 people to 50,

