00:54:48,912 --> 00:54:50,593
My hope is that you take something away from this

895
00:54:50,633 --> 00:54:54,475
that you find useful or inspiring to try and experiment

896
00:54:54,795 --> 00:54:57,336
with in your own studios, whatever the size,

